hotel.hotelName: Wyndham Casablanca Jakarta (Formerly The Park Lane Jakarta)
hotel.description: The 5-star The Park Lane Jakarta offers comfort and convenience whether you're on business or holiday in Jakarta. Offering a variety of facilities and services, the hotel provides all you need for a good night's sleep. Facilities like 24-hour room service, free Wi-Fi in all rooms, 24-hour security, taxi service, daily housekeeping are readily available for you to enjoy. Designed for comfort, selected guestrooms offer television LCD/plasma screen, additional bathroom, carpeting, complimentary instant coffee, complimentary tea to ensure a restful night. Take a break from a long day and make use of yoga room, hot tub, fitness center, sauna, outdoor pool. The Park Lane Jakarta is an excellent choice from which to explore Jakarta or to simply relax and rejuvenate.
